      "settings": {
        "heading": "If You Want To Relieve Sciatica And Back Pain… You Must Start With Your Spinal Discs",
        "body_text": "<p>Your spinal discs act as the shock absorbers between your vertebrae, cushioning your spine and protecting your nerves.</p><p>When at full height, you should be able to move and bend without any issues, and your discs should be able to absorb any impact with ease.</p><p>But imagine, as we sit for prolonged periods, work long hours, and grow older…</p><p>Our discs dry out and shrink, forcing the vertebrae closer together and putting pressure on the nerves.</p><p>This is the root cause of Sciatica and the leading reason why back pain and stiffness feel never ending.</p><p>And until you rehydrate your spinal discs, the pain will never truly go away.</p>",
